{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22ed5b310a","title":"转发习仲勋关于西北土改工作情况的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f1301f3bf","index":0,"year":1948,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"22ed5b310a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"bbc75a90b7","name":"习仲勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f47c15c957","type":"paragraph","text":"转发习仲勋关于西北土改工作情况的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"22ed5b310a"},{"id":"9aac432c42","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年1月20日）完全同意习仲勋同志这些意见”。华北、华中各老解放区有同羊情形者，务须密切注意改正“左”的错误。凡犯有“左”的错误的地方，只要领导机关处理得法，儿个星期即可纠正过来，不要推延很久才去纠正。同时注意不要使下面因为纠正“左”而误解为不动。口习仲勋在给毛泽东的报备中提出，由于义合会议潜伏一科“左”的来的地区，多强调“键盛路线”，反对所调“中农路线”，出现乱斗、乱打、孔没收财物，乱担地出门等现象。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"22ed5b310a"}],"page":{"id":"409ef674fb","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"22ed5b310a","start":536,"end":536}}}},"__N_SSG":true}